creator: Deckle App
descriptionHtml:
Task sharing is a new concept pioneered by Deckle, giving you the chance to interact with others by sharing your daily tasks. Make your grocery run, gym/jogging session more interesting by sharing it in real time with your friends and family. They can then give you support by awarding you a medal or drop in to chat!

If you are not ready to share Deckle with friends yet, you can still use it to keep track of your tasks and set deadlines, get a cool surprise when you tap the "done" button!

Deckle will help you build new connections by matching you to a virtual room with people sharing your interests / subjects / course, and giving you the chance to interact with others by sharing your daily tasks.

Make sure to leave feedback and send any feature requests to lex@deckle.app
descriptionShort: Task sharing lets you interact with others by sharing your daily tasks!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Hey Android Decklers! You can support your friends by awarding and chatting with them using the all new exclusive to android chat screen! Get productive guys!

title: Deckle: Task Sharing

creator: Deckle App
descriptionHtml:
Deckle has unique team games you can use to run a fun event in real life with many groups and teams in your community.

The scavenger hunt, or what we call the Incredible race, allows you to create tasks for your participants, such as answering questions, going to places and taking pictures or video and even drawing tasks! What's special, is that every group member will be assigned automatically to a task at least once. That way, everyone is involved!

Make sure to leave feedback and send any feature requests to lex@deckle.app
descriptionShort: Break the ice with personalised games such as trivia, scavenger hunts, etc!
